{
  "stem": "8784.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes that bakery would not have any bread anymore by the time we reached the end of the line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So life became unbearable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was difficult to buy coal for fuel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how we got our heat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kerosene for light, we needed kerosene in those days for our lights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything was in short supply.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as bad as it was, we did not realize immediately that there are worst things to come.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any idea that this would be worse on a daily, weekly basis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, with my whole family not being able to go to school, we were all at home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the situation was more cramped than it was before, because we were all home with no place to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother became the main food supplier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had what they would say at time, an Aryan appearance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she was able to get on a train much easier than my father would be able to do and travel to the country and buy some supplies and bring it home to feed the family.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This became the major occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was able to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, it was-- there wasn't enough work anymore, so it-- money, money was also in short supply and things became much more difficult.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1940, we still lived in, in Borek Falecki.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also by 1941, the order came out that all the Jews from the area, surrounding areas, would have to report to a ghetto, which was now created in-- outside of Krakow in Podgorze.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My family did not immediately follow that order.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
